SipProviderListener
public class SipPromisqueInterface
extends SipInterface

SipPromisqueInterface is the SipInterface for capturing all SIP messages in PROMISQUE mode. All incoming messages are passed to the listener associated to the SipPromisqueInterface regardless of any other opened SipInterface.

More than one SipPromisqueInterface can be open concurrently.
